---
import AuthUnprotected from "../features/auth/AuthUnprotected.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Home">
  <AuthUnprotected>
    <main class="h-screen flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 px-4 max-w-7xl mx-auto md:items-center md:w-[70%] lg:flex-row overflow-y-hidden">
      <div class="space-y-8 max-w-3xl">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-extrabold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-600 to-emerald-500 mb-4 leading-tight">
            SyncSpend<span class="text-emerald-400">.</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-teal-800 font-medium">Control inteligente para pequeñas empresas</p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-1rem text-gray-700 leading-relaxed md:leading-loose">
          En la economía volátil de Venezuela, cada bolívar cuenta. <span class="font-semibold text-teal-600">SyncSpend</span> te ofrece el control total de tus finanzas empresariales: monitoreo multi-moneda, análisis inteligente de gastos y reportes automatizados para tomar decisiones con confianza.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 pt-2">
          <a href="/forms" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-600 to-emerald-500 hover:from-teal-700 hover:to-emerald-600 text-white font-bold py-5 px-10 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 text-lg text-center">
            Comienza ya!
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </AuthUnprotected>
</Layout>